Installation Instructions:
=========================

1. Install dependencies:
pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Turn into executable: 
chmod +x kubectl-search.py

3. Copy to path:
sudo cp kubectl-search.py /usr/local/bin/kubectl-search


Usage:
======

kubectl search arg1 arg2

Examples:
kubectl search farmId -Low5
kubectl search far -Lo
kubectl search dst constancia
kubectl search gro Mnu